I've made lots of souffles and they've always come out perfect. Unfortunately, this was not one of them. Not sure what went wrong but they barely rose and then fell before the cooking time was over. Loved the flavor but missed the souffle texture.

Rating: 2
I did something seriously wrong (maybe because I don't have a thermometer to make sure I was cooking at the right temperature) and the souffles never rose. Instead, after baking they came out similar to the base of a lemon meringue pie! Nevertheless, my husband thought they were good and said I should make the recipe again exactly the same way.

